In the years of peace before the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], the '''Jinzler family''' lived on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], in the shadow of the [[Jedi Temple/Legends|Jedi Temple]]. The Jinzler parents worked at the Temple itself, as maintenance engineers on the electrical equipment. They adored and honored the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] and took each of their children in to be tested for potential [[The Force/Legends|Force]] sensitivity. The third Jinzler child, [[Lorana Jinzler|Lorana]], was accepted for Jedi training at the age of 10 months. The fourth child, [[Dean Jinzler|Dean]], was a gifted engineer,<ref name="Outbound Flight" /> and would later visit the site of his sister's death.<ref name="Survivor's Quest" />

